page.title: 09ECOLOGY
page.content: Ecology There are 5 woods in our block-Nobles wood Sands plantation, Holton park, Water lane plantation and Lodge plantation.Holton park is the largest wood and nobles wood the smallest.There is a mixture of deciduous and evergreen.There are a lot of oak trees and fir trees.Mr.Dunn looks after the Holton park and makes sure that new trees are planted. Mrs.Foster who lives in Holton village has prepared a very full and interesting list of the flora in Holton-le-Moor.Unfortunately this was to long to include but is available to anyone interested from the school.
